'''40251A''' was a bylaw established by the leaders of the resort city [[Le Yer]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Abregado-rae/Legends|Abregado-rae]]. It outlawed the operation of illegally modified [[Starship/Legends|starships]] in the airspace immediately surrounding the resort.<ref name="WEG">{{WEGCite|story=Abregado-Rae Intrigue|book=No Disintegrations (West End Games)}}</ref>

